embeds.title: Welcome to the <:ves:1052452322757845083> VES Washington Section Discord
embeds.description:
Welcome to this unofficial [Visual Effects Society](https://www.vesglobal.org/) Discord server,  run by volunteers from the Washington Section of the Visual Effects Society.   Members from other sections (and non-members that are just fans of VFX) are all welcome to join us.

**VES Members**:  Drop us a message in <#1053558396852375624> and we will grant you access to the <#1052026545180528702> channels.
